params._collateralToken: The address of the ERC20 token to be used as collateral for new vaults.
params._initialOwner: The initial owner of the factory contract.
params._oracleManager: The address of the OracleManager contract to be used in new vaults.
params._sccUsdToken: The address of the SCC-USD stablecoin token to be used in new vaults.

returns.vaultAddress: The address of the newly created Vault.

owner().details: Returns the address of the current owner.

renounceOwnership().details: Leaves the contract without owner. It will not be possible to call `onlyOwner` functions. Can only be called by the current owner. NOTE: Renouncing ownership will leave the contract without an owner, thereby disabling any functionality that is only available to the owner.

transferOwnership(address).details: Transfers ownership of the contract to a new account (`newOwner`). Can only be called by the current owner.

collateralToken().notice: The address of the ERC20 token used as collateral for new vaults.

createNewVault().notice: Creates a new Vault for the caller and transfers ownership to them.

oracleManager().notice: The address of the OracleManager contract to be used in new vaults.

sccUsdToken().notice: The address of the SCC-USD stablecoin token to be used in new vaults.
